channel.title: Server help!
channel.description:
well yeah..i dreamed to make an rsps. i tried coding 300+,400+,500+,600+,700+ and yeah it went well....but the problem is i cant portforward...when i type in 192.168.1.1 ....it says i need admin and password... i tried all the possible passwords like admin and admin and man mmore..i tried asking to my parents but they said they didnt even changed it..my router is cisco E1000 . .i also tried portforwarding with hamachi but i cant install it becuz i need admin priviledges..... i also tried reseting my router yet nothing changed....
can any one here help me make a server? ....... if you can host it ..well be a team.. ill help you grow the rsps.. im good at: coding some 300+ and 700+ a good html web designer.... im friendly and active always..
if you are interested to help me host the server.. please add me on skype: theepicpker requirements: very active, computer that has less lag and a good cpu performance.
thanks for reading this post.. if i ever post this topic in a wrong board, please inform me and ill move it ^_^
